column5: I was at Canadian Tire and saw this!    I thought it was pretty funny and wanted to share I'm totally considering this as a christmas gift now.. haha well, maybe.   edit: added a link.. http://www.canadiantire.ca/browse/product_...fromSearch=true
I saw that lamp at Crappy Tire in Fenelon Falls in the spring and really liked it. My wife got it for me for my birthday. It is now my nightlight in the bedroom at the cottage. It fits in real nice.
Would go well with TJ's toilet  Maureen
